Title: VOLTME 20W Double USB-C  Charger
Description:
20W Fast Charger 3X Faster: VOLTME USB C plug equipped with a max current of 3A that can charge your device with fast speed. 20W USB-C charging gives you the power you need to charge up your Smartphone to 50% in about 30 minutes - that’s up to 3 times faster than your old 5W charger.

  • Charge 2 Devices Simultaneously: The VOLTME Multi USB Plug can charge your gadgets through the night, it won't take up a lot of space on your desk or nightstand, the charger 2 in 1 offers 2 ports USB-C suitable for iPhone, AirPods, and other compatible devices while you sleep.

  • Travel Ready: VOLTME USB-C Power Adapter is perfect for office, home or travel use. With a minimalist design, this charger is easy to carry while you travel with it. It is small, light and therefore perfect for your luggage.

  • Safe & Reliable: A safer charger for your devices. There are tons of safety protections built right in which ensure safe charging of your devices no matter what the situation. Overvoltage, overheating, short circuit protection and industry safety certifications UKCA, RoHS and FCC ensure safety with a dependable V-Dynamic construction.

  • Maximum Compatibility: This power adapter PD 3.0 & PPS fast charger supports multi-voltage charging at 5V, 9V, 12V output 20W Max, ensuring universal compatibility with most phones & tablets - iPad Pro/iPad Air/iPad mini, Galaxy Note 8/9/10, applicable for iPhone 14 / 13 / 13 mini / 13 Pro / 13 Pro Max, etc.

  • What You Get: VOLTME USB C charger, recyclable box, welcome guide, 18-month warranty, and premium after-sales service. (cable not included).

Title: VOLTME 30W Double USB-C Charger
Description:
VOLTME 30W USB Charger: VOLTME's 30W dual USB port charger allows you to charge two devices simultaneously. Get optimal charging capacity for your device with one QC3.0 port and get another smart USB-C PD port simultaneously.

  • Powered by GaN III Technology: GaN semiconductors are considerably faster and safer than traditional silicon. They’re particularly efficient at switching, which they do 20 times faster. They also draw 40% less energy, so your charger isn’t wasting nearly as much extra juice.

  • Durable and safe: With up to 30W power, the VOLTME type c plug supply has a lifespan of more than 30,000 hours. It supports charging Macbook Air, tablets, iPhones and other devices with overvoltage, overheating and short-circuit protection to keep connected devices safe.

  • Travel Ready: VOLTME USB-C plug is perfect for office, home or travel use. With a minimalist design, this charger is easy to carry while you travel with it. It is small and light at 60g, therefore perfect for your luggage.

  • What You Get: VOLTME USB Plug Adaptor UK 30W, recyclable box, welcome guide, 18-month warranty, and premium after-sales service. (cable not included).
